OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatives are set to
OL,7,Fpublish their manifesto with a focus
OL,8,Fon income tax and cutting benefits
OL,9,Fbills.
OL,11,FThe party is set to launch the
OL,12,Fmanifesto in Edinburgh on Tuesday with
OL,13,FConservative leader Russell Findlay
OL,14,Fexpected to focus on the cost-of-
OL,15,Fliving crisis.
OL,17,FMr Findlay is expected to say: "We
OL,18,Fneed to get Scotland working after
OL,19,Falmost two dismal decades of SNP
OL,20,Fincompetence, failure and scandal.
OL,26,@yD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
