OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775537898
OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,F"Things do not have to be this bad.
OL,7,FThe mess that Scotland is in is the
OL,8,Fresult of the wrong political choices
OL,9,Fmade by SNP administrations.
OL,11,F"Our manifesto shows there can be a
OL,12,Fdifferent way ` a brighter, more
OL,13,Fprosperous way for everyone.
OL,15,F"A lower-tax Scotland, where people
OL,16,Fcan keep and spend more of the money
OL,17,Fthey graft for."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
