OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatives have said
OL,7,Fthey would cut income tax by raising
OL,8,Fthe point at which workers start
OL,9,Fpaying, creating one lower rate of 19%
OL,10,Fand ending the freeze on the higher-
OL,11,Frate threshold.
OL,13,FThey have said the tax cuts will be
OL,14,Fpaid for by the party's pledge to
OL,15,Fscrap #7 billion in benefits bills and
OL,16,Freducing government bureaucracy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
