OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,FMr Findlay is expected to continue: "A
OL,7,Fbooming Scotland, where businesses can
OL,8,Fthrive. A functioning Scotland,
OL,9,Fgenerating the revenue we need to
OL,10,Fcreate infrastructure and public
OL,11,Fservices fit for the 21st century.
OL,13,F"That is our Conservative way.
OL,15,F"This manifesto is our most detailed
OL,16,Fplan ever for making that vision a
OL,17,Freality. It is comprehensive, costed
OL,18,Fand credible.
OL,26,@nD@eOUuD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
