PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775537898
OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,F"John Swinney has been crystal clear
OL,7,Fthat he will use an SNP majority to
OL,8,Fpress ahead with his plan to hold a
OL,9,Fsecond, unwanted, divisive referendum
OL,10,Fon breaking up our country.
OL,12,F"We cannot allow him to plunge the
OL,13,Fnext parliament into constitutional
OL,14,Fchaos.
OL,16,F"We cannot allow any distraction from
OL,17,Fthe issues that matter most to people:
OL,18,Fhelping with the cost-of-living
OL,19,Fcrisis, growing the economy and fixing
OL,20,Four broken public services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
