OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,F"Every vote for the Scottish
OL,7,FConservatives on the peach-coloured
OL,8,Fballot paper will take us a step
OL,9,Fcloser to stopping the SNP."
OL,11,FSNP candidate for Banffshire and
OL,12,FBuchan Coast, Karen Adam, said: "Did
OL,13,FRussell Findlay also find his decision
OL,14,Fto back Liz Truss to the hilt as she
OL,15,Fdestroyed the economy 'costed and
OL,16,Fcredible'? There is nothing credible
OL,17,Fabout anything Russell Findlay has to
OL,18,Fsay.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]tD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
