OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775537898
OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,F"The Tories, the Labour Party and
OL,7,FReform have nothing to offer the
OL,8,FScottish people and we know Anas
OL,9,FSarwar is plotting a dodgy deal with
OL,10,Fthe pair of them.
OL,12,F"Only the SNP is on Scotland's side
OL,13,Fwith John Swinney's strong leadership
OL,14,Ffirmly focused on the priorities of
OL,15,Fthe people of Scotland ` our NHS, the
OL,16,Fcost-of-living crisis and offering
OL,17,Fpeople hope through a fresh start with
OL,18,Findependence."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@NO]
