OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,FScottish Labour deputy leader Jackie
OL,7,FBaillie said the Tories were just
OL,8,F"going through the motions" despite
OL,9,Fbeing "utterly irrelevant" in this
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,F"Russell Findlay and co were
OL,13,Fcheerleading for Liz Truss while she
OL,14,Fcrashed the economy so it's no wonder
OL,15,Fvoters are turning away from the
OL,16,FScottish Tories in their droves," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"It's clearer than ever that only
OL,20,FScottish Labour can beat the SNP and
OL,21,Fdeliver the change Scotland needs.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@[O]qD@GOUqD@ZO]tD@AOUxD@aO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU
