OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,F"While the height of the Scottish
OL,7,FTories' ambition is to deprive the SNP
OL,8,Fof a majority, Scottish Labour is
OL,9,Ffighting to remove them from
OL,10,Fgovernment entirely.
OL,12,F"Russell Findlay is happy to play John
OL,13,FSwinney's game and is trying to drag
OL,14,Fthis election back to the arguments of
OL,15,Fthe past because he has nothing to say
OL,16,Fabout our future.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
