OL,3,CScottish Tory manifesto to launch with
OL,4,Cfocus on tax and cutting benefits bills
OL,6,F"The momentum is behind Scottish
OL,7,FLabour because we are the only party
OL,8,Fthat can get rid of this failing SNP
OL,9,Fgovernment and fix the mess they have
OL,10,Fmade of our NHS, our schools, our
OL,11,Fjustice system and our economy."
